Invocation Name: san jose guide
des: One stop guide to all the fun and attractions in this San Francisco bay area city of San Jose, California. This guide includes top 5 attractions, local news (data provided by New York Times) and other places such as parks, muesums with lots of learning and fun for kids and adults alike. You can also find the contact e-mail and phone numbers on the Alexa app on your devices - app on your smartphones or on your FireTV screen. Alexa is all excited to take you on a journey to this amazing, culturally rich, fun-filled Silicon Valley capital of San Jose, California.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
